article_title: Check Health Care Compliance Before Tax Season Kicks Off, Official Says > U.S. DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE > Article View

article_metadata.DESCRIPTION: The Defense Department wants its service members and civilian employees to know it’s not too early to make sure their 2015 health insurance paperwork is in order before filing their federal taxes.,
